name: Warmup_Div02_Sub01
queryText:
SELECT DISTINCT
GmailD2S1.CPF,
GmailD2S1.NOME,
GmailD2S1.EMAIL,
GmailD2S1.EMAIL_VALIDO,
CASE

  WHEN CHARINDEX(' ', GmailD2S1.NOME) = 0 THEN GmailD2S1.NOME

  ELSE SUBSTRING( GmailD2S1.NOME , 1, CHARINDEX(' ', GmailD2S1.NOME) )

END AS PNOME
FROM Gmail_DIV02_SUB01 GmailD2S1
UNION
